OL,3,CDad describes 'terrifying' moment a
OL,4,Clandslide swept through home
OL,6,FA father has described the
OL,7,F"terrifying" moment a landslide caused
OL,8,Fby Storm Bert swept through his home
OL,9,Fwith his family inside.
OL,11,FEndaf Owens, four other adults and six
OL,12,Fyoung children had to be rescued when
OL,13,Fa torrent of water and debris washed
OL,14,Fthrough their farm, causing severe
OL,15,Fdamage.
OL,17,FIt's thought it could be 18 months
OL,18,Fbefore they can return to the land
OL,19,Fthey have farmed in Llanarmon Dyffryn
OL,20,FCeiriog, Wrexham county, for more than
OL,21,F40 years.
