OL,3,CDad describes 'terrifying' moment a
OL,4,Clandslide swept through home
OL,6,FEndaf said the experience was
OL,7,F"terrifying" and the family had been
OL,8,F"very lucky" to escape.
OL,10,FHis wife and his sister had just
OL,11,Fbrought the children back into the
OL,12,Fhouse on Saturday, 23 November, when
OL,13,Fthe landslide came through the
OL,14,Fkitchen. One of his children narrowly
OL,15,Favoided getting seriously hurt.
OL,17,F"She's got a few scratches on her
OL,18,Fface, but she's okay," Endaf said.
