OL,6,FEndaf had been away from the rest of
OL,7,Fhis family at the time tending to the
OL,8,Fsheep on higher ground.
OL,10,F"I came down from the top road and saw
OL,11,Fthis - it was terrifying, really," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FHe added that it will be between 12-18
OL,15,Fmonths before the family can return to
OL,16,Ftheir home after the devastation
OL,17,Fcaused.
