OL,6,FFriends have arranged for the family
OL,7,Fto stay in a nearby bed and breakfast
OL,8,Fin the meantime, while the local
OL,9,Fcommunity has rallied around the
OL,10,Ffamily, with neighbours helping to
OL,11,Fevacuate them on the day.
OL,13,FMike Crawshaw, one of those
OL,14,Fneighbours, said there was "utter
OL,15,Fdevastation" when he arrived at the
OL,16,Ffarm after seeing sets of lights and
OL,17,Fnoticing he had a missed call from his
OL,18,Fneighbours.
