OL,3,CDad describes 'terrifying' moment a
OL,4,Clandslide swept through home
OL,6,F"The water (...) was several feet
OL,7,Fdeep," he told ITV Cymru Wales. "When
OL,8,Fyou saw the devastation, you just hope
OL,9,Fthat everyone's safe. It was
OL,10,Fhorrendous."
OL,12,FMike and another neighbour took the
OL,13,Ffamily in tractors down to a nearby
OL,14,Fpub to stay warm.
OL,16,F"The community are unbelievable,"
OL,17,FEndaf said. "I can't thank them
OL,18,Fenough. It's quite overwhelming, to be
OL,19,Fhonest."
