OL,6,FCouncillor Trevor Bates praised the
OL,7,Fefforts of the local community in
OL,8,Fassisting the family.
OL,10,F"It's emotional - the people have been
OL,11,Fso fantastic," he said.
OL,13,FStorm Bert brought torrential rain at
OL,14,Fthe weekend, with a total of 433
OL,15,Fproperties were impacted across Wales,
OL,16,Fas well as infrastructure, after the
OL,17,Fsubstantial wind and rain brought by
OL,18,FStorm Bert.
